      "content": "hey i need to ask u something serious. i think someone or something is using my digital identity against me. i just saw a post on my linkedin and twitter that looks exactly like something i'd say but i didnt write it... it's too perfect. like even the way i use emojis and stuff is identical. is it actually possible for an AI to just... take over someone's digital persona so well that no one can tell the difference?",
