      "content": "that's terrifying. i feel like i'm watching a ghost of myself do things online while the real me is just sitting here. if they've actually studied me that much, how would they even get my specific \"vibe\" right? like, is there a way they can just scrape my entire history to build a digital twin that's basically me? i feel like i'm losing control of my own life.",
